data.description: Under Construction. Rare Opportunity to own a Brand New Home in the highly sought after Community of Rainbow Springs Country Club. Enjoy all that Central Florida has to offer as well as world class amenities right in your own neighborhood. This exclusive community boasts direct access to the world renown Rainbow River with a private Swimming Area, Boat Launch, pavillion and more. You can also take advantage of the Community Pool, Clubhouse, Fitness Center, Tennis Courts, Billiards and more. The list of extras goes on and on. The brand new home is located on an over-sized lot. You will fall in love with the Front Porch, Cathedral Ceilings, and Open Floor Plan. Not to mention Upgrades such as Granite Countertops, Luxury Vinyl Plank Flooring, and Tile Showers. All Appliances Included  and you can live worry free with a 10 Year Structural Warranty! Homes like this one don't come along very often. Don't miss out! Pictures are from another model and may not reflect actual color selections/finishings. Some pictures have been virtually staged. Garage orientation, colors, or finishes may vary for actual home. Information is deemed accurate, but no guarantee is made.
